This error can occur when the timeout specified was too short, or a connection to the server or proxy cannot be established.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-1074">請確定伺服器和 Proxy URL 都正確。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1074">Ensure that the server and proxy URL are correct.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1618">0xC001F185</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1618">0xC001F185</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1619">-1073614459</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1619">-1073614459</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1620">DTS_E_NOEVALEXPRESSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1620">DTS_E_NOEVALEXPRESSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1621">For 迴圈 "%1" 上的評估條件運算式是空的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1621">The evaluation condition expression on the For Loop "%1" is empty.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-1622">For 迴圈中必須有布林值評估運算式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1622">There must be a Boolean evaluation expression in the For Loop.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1627">0xC001F187</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1627">0xC001F187</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1628">-1073614457</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1628">-1073614457</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1629">DTS_E_EXPREVALASSIGNMENTTOREADONLYVARIABLE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1629">DTS_E_EXPREVALASSIGNMENTTOREADONLYVARIABLE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1630">在指派運算式中使用唯讀變數 "%1" 時發生錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1630">Error using a read-only variable "%1" in an assignment expression.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-1631">運算式結果無法指派給變數，因為變數是唯讀的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1631">The expression result cannot be assigned to the variable because the variable is read only.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-1632">請選擇可以寫入的變數，或從這個變數移除運算式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1632">Choose a variable that can be written to, or remove the expression from this variable.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1633">0xC001F188</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1633">0xC001F188</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1634">-1073614456</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1634">-1073614456</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1635">DTS_E_EXPREVALASSIGNMENTVARIABLELOCKFORWRITEFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1635">DTS_E_EXPREVALASSIGNMENTVARIABLELOCKFORWRITEFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1636">無法評估運算式 "%1"，因為變數 "%2" 不存在或無法存取進行寫入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1636">Cannot evaluate expression "%1" because the variable "%2" does not exist or cannot be accessed for writing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-1637">運算式結果無法指派給變數，因為找不到變數，或無法鎖定變數進行寫入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1637">The expression result cannot be assigned to the variable because the variable was not found, or could not be locked for write access.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1642">0xC001F18A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1642">0xC001F18A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1643">-1073614454</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1643">-1073614454</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1644">DTS_E_EXPREVALRESULTTYPECONVERSIONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1644">DTS_E_EXPREVALRESULTTYPECONVERSIONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-1645">將運算式 "%1" 的結果從類型 "%2" 轉換成支援的類型失敗，錯誤碼為 0x%3!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1645">The conversion of the result of the expression"%1" from type "%2" to a supported type failed with error code 0x%3!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-1646">嘗試將運算式結果轉換成執行階段引擎支援的類型時，即使支援類型轉換，仍然發生意外的錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-1646">An unexpected error occurred when trying to convert the expression result to a type supported by the runtime engine, even though the type conversion is supported.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4103">0xC0047021</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4103">0xC0047021</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4104">-1073450975</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4104">-1073450975</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4105">DTS_E_THREADFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4105">DTS_E_THREADFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4106">SSIS 錯誤碼 DTS_E_THREADFAILED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4106">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_THREADFAILED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4107">"%1" 執行緒已結束，錯誤碼為 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4107">Thread "%1" has exited with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4108">在此之前可能已公佈過錯誤訊息，說明執行緒為何結束的詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4108">There may be error messages posted before this with more information on why the thread has exited.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4109">0xC0047022</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4109">0xC0047022</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4110">-1073450974</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4110">-1073450974</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4111">DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4111">DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4112">SSIS 錯誤碼 DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4112">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4113">處理輸入 "%4" (%5!d!) 時，元件 "%1" (%2!d!) 上的 ProcessInput 方法失敗，錯誤碼為 0x%3!8.8X!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4113">The ProcessInput method on component "%1" (%2!d!) failed with error code 0x%3!8.8X!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4114">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4114">while processing input "%4" (%5!d!).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4115">識別的元件從 ProcessInput 方法傳回錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4115">The identified component returned an error from the ProcessInput method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4116">此錯誤是元件特定的錯誤，但屬於嚴重錯誤，將導致資料流程工作停止執行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4116">The error is specific to the component, but the error is fatal and will cause the Data Flow task to stop running.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4117">在此之前可能已公佈過錯誤訊息，說明有關此失敗的詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4117">There may be error messages posted before this with more information about the failure.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4118">0xC0047023</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4118">0xC0047023</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4119">-1073450973</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4119">-1073450973</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4120">DTS_E_CANTREALIZEVIRTUALBUFFERS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4120">DTS_E_CANTREALIZEVIRTUALBUFFERS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4121">無法實現一組虛擬緩衝區。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4121">A set of virtual buffers cannot be realized.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4122">0xC0047024</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4122">0xC0047024</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4123">-1073450972</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4123">-1073450972</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4124">DTS_E_PIPELINETOOCOMPLEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4124">DTS_E_PIPELINETOOCOMPLEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4125">這個管線需要的執行緒數目是 %1!d! 個，已超出 %2!d! 個的系統限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4125">The number of threads required for this pipeline is %1!d!, which is more than the system limit of %2!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4126">為管線設定的執行緒需求數量太多。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4126">The pipeline requires too many threads as configured.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4127">可能是非同步輸出太多，或 EngineThreads 屬性設定太高。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4127">There are either too many asynchronous outputs, or EngineThreads property is set too high.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4128">請將管線拆解成多個封裝，或降低 EngineThreads 屬性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4128">Split the pipeline into multiple packages, or reduce the value of the EngineThreads property.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4133">0xC0047029</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4133">0xC0047029</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4134">-1073450967</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4134">-1073450967</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4135">DTS_E_SCHEDULERCOULDNOTCOUNTDESTINATIONS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4135">DTS_E_SCHEDULERCOULDNOTCOUNTDESTINATIONS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4136">資料流程引擎排程器無法取得配置中的目的地計數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4136">The Data Flow engine scheduler cannot obtain a count of the destinations in the layout.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4137">0xC004702A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4137">0xC004702A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4138">-1073450966</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4138">-1073450966</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4139">DTS_E_COMPONENTVIEWISUNAVAILABLE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4139">DTS_E_COMPONENTVIEWISUNAVAILABLE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4140">元件檢視無法使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4140">The component view is unavailable.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4141">請確定已經建立元件檢視。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4141">Make sure the component view has been created.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4142">0xC004702B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4142">0xC004702B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4143">-1073450965</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4143">-1073450965</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4144">DTS_E_INCORRECTCOMPONENTVIEWID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4144">DTS_E_INCORRECTCOMPONENTVIEWID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4145">元件檢視識別碼不正確。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4145">The component view ID is incorrect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4146">元件檢視可能並未同步。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4146">The component view may be out of synchronization.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4147">請嘗試釋放元件檢視再重新建立。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4147">Try releasing the component view and recreating it.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4148">0xC004702C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4148">0xC004702C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4149">-1073450964</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4149">-1073450964</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4150">DTS_E_BUFFERNOTLOCKED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4150">DTS_E_BUFFERNOTLOCKED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4151">這個緩衝區未鎖定，無法操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4151">This buffer is not locked and cannot be manipulated.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4158">0xC004702E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4158">0xC004702E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4159">-1073450962</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4159">-1073450962</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4160">DTS_E_CANTREGISTERBUFFERTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4160">DTS_E_CANTREGISTERBUFFERTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4161">資料流程工作無法註冊緩衝區類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4161">The Data Flow task cannot register a buffer type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4162">類型具有 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4162">The type had %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4163">個資料行，且已用於 %2!d!. 執行樹狀目錄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4163">columns and was for execution tree %2!d!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4164">0xC004702F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4164">0xC004702F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4165">-1073450961</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4165">-1073450961</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4166">DTS_E_INVALIDUSESDISPOSITIONSVALUE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4166">DTS_E_INVALIDUSESDISPOSITIONSVALUE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4167">UsesDispositions 屬性無法變更初始值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4167">The UsesDispositions property cannot be changed from its initial value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4168">當編輯 XML 且修改 UsesDispositions 值時，就會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4168">This occurs when the XML is edited and the UsesDispositions value is modified.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4169">這個值是在元件加入封裝時設定，不允許變更。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4169">This value is set by the component when it is added to the package and is not allowed to change.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4170">0xC0047030</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4170">0xC0047030</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4171">-1073450960</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4171">-1073450960</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4172">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDINITIALIZE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4172">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDINITIALIZE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4173">資料流程工作無法初始化必要的執行緒，無法開始執行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4173">The Data Flow task failed to initialize a required thread and cannot begin execution.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4174">執行緒先前已報告特定錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4174">The thread previously reported a specific error.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4175">0xC0047031</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4175">0xC0047031</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4176">-1073450959</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4176">-1073450959</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4177">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDCREATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4177">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDCREATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4178">資料流程工作無法建立必要的執行緒，無法開始執行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4178">The Data Flow task failed to create a required thread and cannot begin running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4179">當發生記憶體不足的狀況時，通常會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4179">The usually occurs when there is an out-of-memory state.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4180">0xC0047032</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4180">0xC0047032</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4181">-1073450958</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4181">-1073450958</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4182">DTS_E_EXECUTIONTREECYCLEADDINGSYNCHRONOUSINPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4182">DTS_E_EXECUTIONTREECYCLEADDINGSYNCHRONOUSINPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4183">"%1" 的同步輸入無法設定為 "%2"，因為會造成循環。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4183">The synchronous input of "%1" cannot be set to "%2" because a cycle would be created.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4184">0xC0047033</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4184">0xC0047033</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4185">-1073450957</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4185">-1073450957</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4186">DTS_E_INVALIDCUSTOMPROPERTYNAME</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4186">DTS_E_INVALIDCUSTOMPROPERTYNAME</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4187">名稱為 "%1" 的自訂屬性無效，因為已存在這個名稱的內建屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4187">A custom property named "%1" is invalid because there is a stock property with that name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4188">在相同物件上，自訂屬性的名稱不能與內建屬性的名稱相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4188">A custom property cannot have the same name as a stock property on the same object.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4189">0xC0047035</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4189">0xC0047035</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4190">-1073450955</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4190">-1073450955</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4191">DTS_E_BUFFERLOCKUNDERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4191">DTS_E_BUFFERLOCKUNDERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4192">緩衝區已經解除鎖定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4192">The buffer was already unlocked.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4193">0xC0047036</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4193">0xC0047036</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4194">-1073450954</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4194">-1073450954</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4195">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALCACHEINTERFACESFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4195">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALCACHEINTERFACESFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4196">%1 初始化失敗，傳回錯誤碼 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4196">%1 failed initialization and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4197">0xC0047037</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4197">0xC0047037</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4198">-1073450953</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4198">-1073450953</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4199">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALRELEASEINTERFACESFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4199">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALRELEASEINTERFACESFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4200">%1 在關閉期間失敗，傳回錯誤碼 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4200">%1 failed during shut down and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4201">元件無法釋放其介面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4201">A component failed to release its interfaces.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4202">0xC0047038</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4202">0xC0047038</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4203">-1073450952</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4203">-1073450952</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4204">DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4204">DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4205">SSIS 錯誤碼 DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4205">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4206">在 %1 上的 PrimeOutput 方法傳回錯誤碼 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4206">The PrimeOutput method on %1 returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4207">當管線引擎呼叫 PrimeOutput() 時，元件傳回失敗碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4207">The component returned a failure code when the pipeline engine called PrimeOutput().</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4208">失敗碼的意義由元件定義，但屬於嚴重錯誤，管線已停止執行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4208">The meaning of the failure code is defined by the component, but the error is fatal and the pipeline stopped executing.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4209">在此之前可能已公佈過錯誤訊息，說明有關此失敗的詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4209">There may be error messages posted before this with more information about the failure.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4210">0xC0047039</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4210">0xC0047039</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4211">-1073450951</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4211">-1073450951</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4212">DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4212">DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4213">SSIS 錯誤碼 DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4213">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4214">"%1" 執行緒收到關閉信號，正在結束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4214">Thread "%1" received a shutdown signal and is terminating.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4215">使用者已要求關閉，或另一個執行緒的錯誤造成管線關閉。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4215">The user requested a shutdown, or an error in another thread is causing the pipeline to shutdown.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4216">在此之前可能已公佈過錯誤訊息，說明執行緒為何取消的詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4216">There may be error messages posted before this with more information on why the thread was cancelled.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4424">0xC0047072</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4424">0xC0047072</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4425">-1073450894</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4425">-1073450894</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4426">DTS_E_OBJECTIDNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4426">DTS_E_OBJECTIDNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4427">不存在識別碼為 %1!d! 的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4427">No object exists with the ID %1!d!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4428">0xC0047073</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4428">0xC0047073</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4429">-1073450893</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4429">-1073450893</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4430">DTS_E_OBJECTIDLOOKUPFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4430">DTS_E_OBJECTIDLOOKUPFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4431">因為錯誤碼 0x%2!8.8X!，找不到識別碼為 %1!d! 的物件</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4431">Unable to locate an object with ID %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4432">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4432">because of the error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4439">0xC0047075</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4439">0xC0047075</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4440">-1073450891</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4440">-1073450891</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4441">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALPUTEVENTINFOSFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4441">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALPUTEVENTINFOSFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4442">"%1" 無法快取 EventInfos 集合，傳回錯誤碼 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4442">The EventInfos collection could not be cached by "%1" and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4443">0xC0047077</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4443">0xC0047077</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4444">-1073450889</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4444">-1073450889</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4445">DTS_E_DUPLICATEOUTPUTCOLUMNNAMES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4445">DTS_E_DUPLICATEOUTPUTCOLUMNNAMES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4446">"%1" 的名稱重複。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4446">The name for "%1" is a duplicate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4447">所有名稱都必須是唯一的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4447">All names must be unique.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4448">0xC0047078</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4448">0xC0047078</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4449">-1073450888</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4449">-1073450888</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4450">DTS_E_NOOUTPUTCOLUMNFORINPUTCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4450">DTS_E_NOOUTPUTCOLUMNFORINPUTCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4451">輸入資料行 "%1" (%2!d!) 沒有相關聯的輸出資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4451">There is no output column associated with input column "%1" (%2!d!).</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4452">0xC0047079</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4452">0xC0047079</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4453">-1073450887</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4453">-1073450887</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4454">DTS_E_EXCLGRPNOSYNCINP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4454">DTS_E_EXCLGRPNOSYNCINP</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4455">"%1" 具有從根來源延伸的虛擬緩衝區。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4455">"%1" has a virtual buffer extending from a root source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4456">非零的排除群組具有零的同步輸入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4456">There is an exclusion group that is not zero with a synchronous input that is zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4457">0xC004707A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4457">0xC004707A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4458">-1073450886</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4458">-1073450886</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4459">DTS_E_ERROROUTCANTBEONSYNCNONEXCLUSIVEOUTPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4459">DTS_E_ERROROUTCANTBEONSYNCNONEXCLUSIVEOUTPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4460">"%1" 不可以是錯誤輸出，因為錯誤輸出不能放在同步、非獨佔的輸出上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4460">"%1" cannot be an error output because error outputs cannot be placed on synchronous, non-exclusive outputs.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4461">0xC004707B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4461">0xC004707B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4462">-1073450885</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4462">-1073450885</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4463">DTS_E_EXPREVALDIVBYZERO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4463">DTS_E_EXPREVALDIVBYZERO</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4464">發生除以零的錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4464">A divide-by-zero error occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4465">在運算式 "%1" 中，右邊運算元等於零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4465">The right side operand evaluates to zero in the expression "%1".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4466">0xC004707C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4466">0xC004707C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4467">-1073450884</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4467">-1073450884</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4468">DTS_E_EXPREVALLITERALOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4468">DTS_E_EXPREVALLITERALOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4469">常值 "%1" 太大，以致於無法納入類型 %2 中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4469">The literal "%1" is too large to fit into type %2.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4470">常值的大小造成此類型溢位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4470">The magnitude of the literal overflows the type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4471">0xC004707D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4471">0xC004707D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4472">-1073450883</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4472">-1073450883</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4473">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPNUMERICOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4473">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPNUMERICOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4474">在資料類型 %2 和 %3 執行二進位運算 "%1" 的結果，超出數值類型的大小上限。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4474">The result of the binary operation "%1" on data types %2 and %3 exceeds the maximum size for numeric types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4475">運算元類型隱含轉換成數值 (DT_NUMERIC) 結果時，一定會遺失有效位數或小數位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4475">The operand types could not be implicitly cast into a numeric (DT_NUMERIC) result without loss of precision or scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4476">若要執行此運算，必須使用轉換運算子，明確轉換一個或兩個運算元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4476">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4477">0xC004707E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4477">0xC004707E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4478">-1073450882</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4478">-1073450882</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4479">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4479">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4480">二進位運算 "%1" 的結果超出結果資料類型 "%2" 的大小上限。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4480">The result of the binary operation "%1" exceeds the maximum size for result data type "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4481">運算結果的大小造成結果類型溢位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4481">The magnitude of the result of the operation overflows the type of the result.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4482">0xC004707F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4482">0xC004707F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4483">-1073450881</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4483">-1073450881</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4484">DTS_E_EXPREVALFUNCTIONOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4484">DTS_E_EXPREVALFUNCTIONOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4485">函數呼叫 "%1" 的結果太大，以致於無法納入類型 "%2" 中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4485">The result of the function call "%1" is too large to fit in type "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4486">函數呼叫的結果大小會造成運算元類型溢位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4486">The magnitude of the result of the function call overflows the type of the operand.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4487">可能需要明確轉換成較大的類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4487">An explicit cast to a larger type may be required.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4488">0xC0047080</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4488">0xC0047080</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4489">-1073450880</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4489">-1073450880</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4490">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYTYPEMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4490">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYTYPEMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4491">對二元運算子 "%3" 而言，資料類型 "%1" 和 "%2" 不相容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4491">The data types "%1" and "%2" are incompatible for binary operator "%3".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4492">運算元類型無法隱含轉換成運算相容的類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4492">The operand types could not be implicitly cast into compatible types for the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4493">若要執行此運算，必須使用轉換運算子，明確轉換一個或兩個運算元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4493">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4494">0xC0047081</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4494">0xC0047081</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4495">-1073450879</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4495">-1073450879</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4496">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDBINARYTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4496">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDBINARYTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4497">資料類型 "%1" 不能用於二元運算子 "%2"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4497">The data type "%1" cannot be used with binary operator "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4498">運算不支援一或兩個運算元的類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4498">The type of one or both of the operands is not supported for the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4499">若要執行此運算，必須使用轉換運算子，明確轉換一個或兩個運算元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4499">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4500">0xC0047082</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4500">0xC0047082</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4501">-1073450878</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4501">-1073450878</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4502">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYSIGNMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4502">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYSIGNMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4503">在運算 "%2" 中，位元二元運算子 "%1" 的符號不相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4503">There is a sign mismatch for the bitwise binary operator "%1" in operation "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4504">這個運算子的兩個運算元必須同為正數或負數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4504">Both operands for this operator must be positive or negative.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4505">0xC0047083</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4505">0xC0047083</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4506">-1073450877</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4506">-1073450877</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4507">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPERATIONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4507">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPERATIONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4508">二進位運算 "%1" 失敗，錯誤碼為 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4508">The binary operation "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4509">發生內部錯誤，或存在記憶體不足的狀況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4509">An internal error occurred, or an out-of-memory condition exists.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4572">0xC0047091</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4572">0xC0047091</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4573">-1073450863</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4573">-1073450863</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4574">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDNULLPARAMTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4574">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDNULLPARAMTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4575">在函數 NULL 中，資料類型為 "%2" 的參數編號 %1!d! 不是整數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4575">Parameter number %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4576">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4576">of the function NULL with data type "%2" is not an integer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4577">NULL() 的參數必須是整數或可以轉換成整數的類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4577">A parameter of NULL() must be an integer or a type that can be converted to an integer.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4596">0xC0047095</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4596">0xC0047095</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4597">-1073450859</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4597">-1073450859</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4598">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCAST</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4598">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCAST</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4599">運算式 "%1" 無法從資料類型 "%2" 轉換成資料類型 "%3"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4599">Cannot cast expression "%1" from data type "%2" to data type "%3".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4600">不支援要求的轉換。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4600">The requested cast is not supported.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4607">0xC0047097</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4607">0xC0047097</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4608">-1073450857</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4608">-1073450857</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4609">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNEXPECTEDPARSEERROR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4609">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNEXPECTEDPARSEERROR</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4610">剖析運算式 "%1" 時發生錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4610">An error occurred when parsing the expression "%1".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4611">未知的原因導致運算式剖析失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4611">The expression failed to parse for an unknown reason.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4612">0xC0047098</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4612">0xC0047098</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4613">-1073450856</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4613">-1073450856</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4614">DTS_E_EXPREVALFAILEDTOPARSEEXPRESSIONWITHHR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4614">DTS_E_EXPREVALFAILEDTOPARSEEXPRESSIONWITHHR</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4615">嘗試剖析運算式 "%1" 失敗，傳回錯誤碼 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4615">Attempt to parse the expression "%1" failed and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4616">無法剖析運算式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4616">The expression cannot be parsed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4617">可能包含無效的元素或格式不正確。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4617">It might contain invalid elements or it might not be well-formed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4618">也可能發生記憶體不足的錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4618">There may also be an out-of-memory error.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4619">0xC0047099</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4619">0xC0047099</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4620">-1073450855</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4620">-1073450855</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4621">DTS_E_EXPREVALFAILEDTOPARSEEXPRESSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4621">DTS_E_EXPREVALFAILEDTOPARSEEXPRESSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4622">運算式 "%1" 無效，無法剖析。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4622">The expression "%1" is not valid and cannot be parsed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4623">運算式可能包含無效元素或格式不正確。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4623">The expression may contain invalid elements or it may not be well-formed.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4624">0xC004709A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4624">0xC004709A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4625">-1073450854</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4625">-1073450854</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4626">DTS_E_EXPREVALEXPRESSIONEMPTY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4626">DTS_E_EXPREVALEXPRESSIONEMPTY</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4627">沒有可以計算的運算式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4627">There was no expression to compute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4628">嘗試計算或取得空運算式的字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4628">An attempt was made to compute or get the string of an empty expression.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4629">0xC004709B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4629">0xC004709B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4630">-1073450853</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4630">-1073450853</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4631">DTS_E_EXPREVALCOMPUTEFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4631">DTS_E_EXPREVALCOMPUTEFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4632">嘗試計算運算式 "%1" 失敗，錯誤碼為 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4632">Attempt to compute the expression "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4638">0xC004709D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4638">0xC004709D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4639">-1073450851</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4639">-1073450851</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4640">DTS_E_EXPREVALCANNOTCONVERTRESULT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4640">DTS_E_EXPREVALCANNOTCONVERTRESULT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4641">無法將運算式結果資料類型 "%1" 轉換成資料行資料類型 "%2"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4641">Cannot convert the expression result data type "%1" to the column data type "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4642">運算式的結果應該寫入輸入/輸出資料行，但運算式的資料類型無法轉換成資料行的資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4642">The result of the expression should be written to an input/output column, but the data type of the expression cannot be converted to the data type of the column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4643">0xC004709E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4643">0xC004709E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4644">-1073450850</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4644">-1073450850</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4645">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPINVALIDCONDITIONTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4645">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPINVALIDCONDITIONTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4646">條件運算子的條件運算式 "%1" 具有無效的資料類型 "%2"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4646">The conditional expression "%1" of the conditional operator has an invalid data type of "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4647">條件運算子的條件運算式必須傳回布林值，也就是類型 DT_BOOL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4647">The conditional expression of the conditional operator must return a Boolean, which is type DT_BOOL.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4648">0xC004709F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4648">0xC004709F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4649">-1073450849</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4649">-1073450849</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4650">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPTYPEMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4650">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPTYPEMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4651">對條件運算子而言，資料類型 "%1" 和 "%2" 不相容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4651">The data types "%1" and "%2" are incompatible for the conditional operator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4652">運算元類型無法隱含轉換成條件運算相容的類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4652">The operand types cannot be implicitly cast into compatible types for the conditional operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4653">若要執行此運算，必須使用轉換運算子，明確轉換一個或兩個運算元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4653">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4691">0xC00470A7</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4691">0xC00470A7</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4692">-1073450841</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4692">-1073450841</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4693">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDTOKENSTATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4693">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDTOKENSTATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4694">嘗試剖析運算式 "%1" 失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4694">Attempt to parse the expression "%1" failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4695">運算式可能包含無效 Token、不完整的 Token 或無效元素，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4695">The expression might contain an invalid token, an incomplete token, or an invalid element.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4696">可能是格式不正確，或遺漏部分必要元素，例如括號。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4696">It might not be well-formed, or might be missing part of a required element such as a parenthesis.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4697">0xC00470A8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4697">0xC00470A8</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4698">-1073450840</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4698">-1073450840</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4699">DTS_E_BLANKOUTPUTCOLUMNNAME</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4699">DTS_E_BLANKOUTPUTCOLUMNNAME</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4700">"%1" 的名稱是空白，但名稱不可以是空白。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4700">The name for "%1" is blank, and names cannot be blank.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4701">0xC00470A9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4701">0xC00470A9</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4702">-1073450839</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4702">-1073450839</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4703">DTS_E_HASSIDEEFFECTSWITHSYNCINP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4703">DTS_E_HASSIDEEFFECTSWITHSYNCINP</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4704">"%1" 將 HasSideEffects 屬性設定為 TRUE，但 "%1" 為同步，不能有副作用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4704">The "%1" has the HasSideEffects property set to TRUE, but "%1" is synchronous and cannot have side effects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4705">請將 HasSideEffects 屬性設定為 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4705">Set the HasSideEffects property to FALSE.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4711">0xC00470AB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4711">0xC00470AB</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4712">-1073450837</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4712">-1073450837</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4713">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTPRECISION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4713">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTPRECISION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4714">值 %1!d! 未辨識為有效的存取模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4714">The value %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4715">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4715">specified for the precision parameter of the cast to data type "%2" is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4716">有效位數必須在 %3!d! 到 %4!d! 的範圍內</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4716">Precision must be in the range %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4717">，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4717">to %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4718">但有效位數值超出類型轉換的範圍。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4718">and the precision value is out of range for the type cast.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4719">0xC00470AC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4719">0xC00470AC</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4720">-1073450836</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4720">-1073450836</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4721">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTSCALE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4721">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTSCALE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4722">值 %1!d! 未辨識為有效的存取模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4722">The value %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4723">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4723">specified for the scale parameter of the cast to data type "%2" is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4724">小數位數必須在 %3!d! 到 %4!d! 的範圍內</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4724">The scale must be in the range %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4725">，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4725">to %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4726">但小數位數值超出類型轉換的範圍。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4726">and the scale value is out of range for the type cast.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4727">小數位數不得超出有效位數，且必須為正數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4727">Scale must not exceed precision and must be positive.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4728">0xC00470AD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4728">0xC00470AD</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4729">-1073450835</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4729">-1073450835</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4730">DTS_E_NONSORTEDOUTPUTHASSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4730">DTS_E_NONSORTEDOUTPUTHASSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4731">"%1" 的 IsSorted 屬性為 false，但輸出資料行的 SortKeyPositions 的 %2!lu! 不是零</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4731">The IsSorted property for "%1" is false, but %2!lu!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4732">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4732">of its output columns' SortKeyPositions are non-zero.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4760">0xC00470B5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4760">0xC00470B5</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4761">-1073450827</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4761">-1073450827</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4762">DTS_E_DISTRIBUTORADDFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4762">DTS_E_DISTRIBUTORADDFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4763">因為錯誤 0x%2!8.8X!，散發者無法提供緩衝區給執行緒 "%1"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4763">A distributor failed to give a buffer to thread "%1" because of error 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4764">目標執行緒可能已關閉。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4764">The target thread is probably shutting down.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4770">0xC00470B7</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4770">0xC00470B7</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4771">-1073450825</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4771">-1073450825</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4772">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALHEXESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4772">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALHEXESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4773">字串常值 "%1" 包含不合法的十六進位逸出序列 "\x%2"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4773">The string literal "%1" contains an illegal hexadecimal escape sequence of  "\x%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4774">在運算式評估工具中，字串常值不支援逸出序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4774">The escape sequence is not supported in string literals in the expression evaluator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4775">十六進位逸出序列必須是 \xhhhh 格式，其中 h 是有效的十六進位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4775">The hexadecimal escape sequences must be of the form \xhhhh where h is a valid hexadecimal digit.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4776">0xC00470B8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4776">0xC00470B8</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4777">-1073450824</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4777">-1073450824</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4778">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4778">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4779">字串常值 "%1" 包含不合法的逸出序列 "\\%2!c!"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4779">The string literal "%1" contains an illegal escape sequence of "\\%2!c!".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4780">在運算式評估工具中，字串常值不支援逸出序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4780">The escape sequence is not supported in string literals in the expression evaluator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4781">如果字串中需要反斜線，請使用雙反斜線 "\\\\"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4781">If a backslash is needed in the string, use a double backslash, "\\\\".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4782">0xC00470B9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4782">0xC00470B9</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4783">-1073450823</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4783">-1073450823</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4784">DTS_E_NOOUTPUTCOLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4784">DTS_E_NOOUTPUTCOLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-4785">"%1" 未包含輸出資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4785">"%1" contains no output columns.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-4786">非同步輸出必須包含輸出資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-4786">An asynchronous output must contain output columns.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6442">0xC02020CD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6442">0xC02020CD</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6443">-1071636275</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6443">-1071636275</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6444">DTS_E_TXUNIONALL_NONDANGLINGUNATTACHEDINPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6444">DTS_E_TXUNIONALL_NONDANGLINGUNATTACHEDINPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6445">%1 未附加，但未標示為懸空。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6445">The %1 is not attached but is not marked as dangling.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6446">將標示為懸空。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6446">It will be marked as dangling.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6460">0xC02020D2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6460">0xC02020D2</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6461">-1071636270</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6461">-1071636270</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6462">DTS_E_MISMATCHCOMPONENTCONNECTIONMANAGERLOCALEID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6462">DTS_E_MISMATCHCOMPONENTCONNECTIONMANAGERLOCALEID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6463">不相符的地區設定識別碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6463">Mismatched locale IDs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6464">元件地區設定識別碼 (%1!d!) 不符合連接管理員地區設定識別碼 (%2!d!)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6464">The component locale ID (%1!d!) does not match the connection manager locale ID (%2!d!).</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6465">0xC02020D3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6465">0xC02020D3</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6466">-1071636269</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6466">-1071636269</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6467">DTS_E_LOCALEIDNOTSET</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6467">DTS_E_LOCALEIDNOTSET</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6468">未設定元件地區設定識別碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6468">The component locale ID has not been set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6469">一般檔案配接器需要在一般檔案連接管理員上設定地區設定識別碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6469">Flat file adapters need to have the locale ID on the flat file connection manager set.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6470">0xC02020D4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6470">0xC02020D4</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6471">-1071636268</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6471">-1071636268</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6472">DTS_E_RAWBYTESTOOLONG</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6472">DTS_E_RAWBYTESTOOLONG</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6473">二進位欄位太大。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6473">The binary field is too large.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6474">配接器嘗試讀取長度為 %1!d! 位元組的二進位欄位，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6474">The adapter attempted to read a binary field that was %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6475">但在位移 %3!d! 上，欄位不能超過 %2!d! 位元組</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6475">bytes long, but expected a field no longer than %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6476">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6476">bytes at offset %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6477">當輸入檔無效時，通常會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6477">This usually occurs when the input file is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6478">檔案包含太大的字串長度，以致於無法納入緩衝區資料行中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6478">The file contains a string length that is too large for the buffer column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6479">0xC02020D5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6479">0xC02020D5</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6480">-1071636267</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6480">-1071636267</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6481">DTS_E_TXSAMPLINGINVALIDPCT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6481">DTS_E_TXSAMPLINGINVALIDPCT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6482">對 "%1" 屬性而言，百分比值 %2!ld! 無效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6482">The percentage, %2!ld!, is not valid for the "%1" property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6483">必須介於 0 和 100 之間。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6483">It must be between 0 and 100.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6484">0xC02020D6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6484">0xC02020D6</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6485">-1071636266</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6485">-1071636266</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6486">DTS_E_TXSAMPLINGINVALIDROWS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6486">DTS_E_TXSAMPLINGINVALIDROWS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6487">對 "%1" 屬性而言，資料列數目 %2!ld! 無效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6487">The number of rows, %2!ld!, is not valid for the "%1" property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6488">必須大於 0。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6488">It must be greater than 0.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6796">0xC0204027</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6796">0xC0204027</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6797">-1071628249</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6797">-1071628249</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6798">DTS_E_CANNOTMAPOUTPUTCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6798">DTS_E_CANNOTMAPOUTPUTCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6799">輸出資料行無法對應到外部中繼資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6799">The output column cannot be mapped to an external metadata column.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6804">0xC020402A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6804">0xC020402A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6805">-1071628246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6805">-1071628246</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6806">DTS_E_CANTSETEXTERNALMETADATACOLUMNDATATYPEPROPERTIES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6806">DTS_E_CANTSETEXTERNALMETADATACOLUMNDATATYPEPROPERTIES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6807">%1 不允許設定外部中繼資料行資料類型屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6807">The %1 does not allow setting external metadata column datatype properties.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6808">0xC020402B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6808">0xC020402B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6809">-1071628245</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6809">-1071628245</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6810">DTS_E_IDNOTINPUTNOROUTPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6810">DTS_E_IDNOTINPUTNOROUTPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6811">識別碼 %1!lu! 不是輸入識別碼，也不是輸出識別碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6811">The ID, %1!lu!, is neither an input ID nor an output ID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-6812">指定的識別碼必須是外部中繼資料集合相關的輸入識別碼或輸出識別碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6812">The specified ID must be the input ID or the output ID that the external metadata collection is associated with.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6813">0xC020402C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6813">0xC020402C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6814">-1071628244</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6814">-1071628244</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6815">DTS_E_METADATACOLLECTIONNOTUSED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6815">DTS_E_METADATACOLLECTIONNOTUSED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6816">"%1" 上的外部中繼資料集合標示為未使用，所以無法執行任何作業。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6816">The external metadata collection on "%1" is marked as not used, so no operations can be performed on it.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6817">0xC020402D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6817">0xC020402D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6818">-1071628243</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6818">-1071628243</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6819">DTS_E_NOBUFFERTYPEONSYNCOUTPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6819">DTS_E_NOBUFFERTYPEONSYNCOUTPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-6820">%1 是同步輸出，且無法擷取同步輸出的緩衝區類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-6820">The %1 is a synchronous output and the buffer type cannot be retrieved for a synchronous output.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7007">0xC020801C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7007">0xC020801C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7008">-1071611876</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7008">-1071611876</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7009">DTS_E_CANNOTACQUIRECONNECTIONFROMCONNECTIONMANAGER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7009">DTS_E_CANNOTACQUIRECONNECTIONFROMCONNECTIONMANAGER</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7010">SSIS 錯誤碼 DTS_E_CANNOTACQUIRECONNECTIONFROMCONNECTIONMANAGER。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7010">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_CANNOTACQUIRECONNECTIONFROMCONNECTIONMANAGER.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7011">對 "%1" 連接管理員呼叫 AcquireConnection 方法失敗，錯誤碼為 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7011">The AcquireConnection method call to the connection manager "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7012">在此之前可能已公佈過錯誤訊息，說明 AcquireConnection 方法呼叫為何失敗的詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7012">There may be error messages posted before this with more information on why the AcquireConnection method call failed.</span></span>|
