|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7039">0xC0208024</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7039">0xC0208024</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7040">-1071611868</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7040">-1071611868</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7041">DTS_E_INCORRECTCONNECTIONOBJECTTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7041">DTS_E_INCORRECTCONNECTIONOBJECTTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7042">連接管理員 "%1" 從 AcquireConnection 方法傳回類型不正確的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7042">The connection manager "%1" returned an object of an  incorrect type from the AcquireConnection method.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7043">0xC0208025</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7043">0xC0208025</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7044">-1071611867</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7044">-1071611867</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7045">DTS_E_INPUTCOLPROPERTYNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7045">DTS_E_INPUTCOLPROPERTYNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7046">輸入資料行 "%1" (%2!d!) 上需要 "%3" 屬性，但找不到此屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7046">The "%3" property is required on input column "%1" (%2!d!), but is not found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7047">應該加入遺漏的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7047">The missing property should be added.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7048">0xC0208026</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7048">0xC0208026</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7049">-1071611866</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7049">-1071611866</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7050">DTS_E_EXTRACTORUNREFERENCED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7050">DTS_E_EXTRACTORUNREFERENCED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7051">"%1" 標示為唯讀，但未被其他任何資料行參考。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7051">The "%1" is marked read-only, but is not referenced by any other column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7052">不允許未參考的資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7052">Unreferenced columns are not allowed.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7053">0xC0208027</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7053">0xC0208027</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7054">-1071611865</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7054">-1071611865</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7055">DTS_E_EXTRACTORREFERENCEDCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7055">DTS_E_EXTRACTORREFERENCEDCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7056">"%1" 參考資料行識別碼 %2!d!，但在輸入上找不到此資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7056">The "%1" references column ID %2!d!, and that column is not found on the input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7057">參考指向不存在的資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7057">A reference points to a nonexistent column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7058">0xC0208028</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7058">0xC0208028</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7059">-1071611864</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7059">-1071611864</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7060">DTS_E_EXTRACTORDATACOLUMNNOTBLOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7060">DTS_E_EXTRACTORDATACOLUMNNOTBLOB</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7061">"%1" 參考 "%2"，但此資料行不是 BLOB 類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7061">The "%1" references "%2", and that column is not of a BLOB type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7062">0xC0208029</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7062">0xC0208029</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7063">-1071611863</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7063">-1071611863</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7064">DTS_E_INSERTERREFERENCEDCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7064">DTS_E_INSERTERREFERENCEDCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7065">"%1" 參考輸出資料行識別碼 %2!d!，但在輸出上找不到該資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7065">The "%1" references output column ID %2!d!, and that column is not found on the output.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7066">0xC020802A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7066">0xC020802A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7067">-1071611862</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7067">-1071611862</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7068">DTS_E_INSERTERCANTREAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7068">DTS_E_INSERTERCANTREAD</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7069">讀取檔案 "%1" 失敗，錯誤碼為 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7069">Reading from the file "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7070">0xC020802B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7070">0xC020802B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7071">-1071611861</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7071">-1071611861</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7072">DTS_E_TXSCD_NOTYPEDCOLUMNSATINPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7072">DTS_E_TXSCD_NOTYPEDCOLUMNSATINPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7073">在緩時變維度轉換的輸入上，至少必須有一個固定、變更或歷程記錄類型的資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7073">There must be at least one column of Fixed, Changing, or Historical type on the input of a Slowly Changing Dimension transform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7074">請確認至少有一個資料行是 FixedAttribute、ChangingAttribute 或 HistoricalAttribute。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7074">Verify that at least one column is a FixedAttribute, ChangingAttribute, or HistoricalAttribute.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7075">0xC020802C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7075">0xC020802C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7076">-1071611860</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7076">-1071611860</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7077">DTS_E_TXSCD_INVALIDINPUTCOLUMNTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7077">DTS_E_TXSCD_INVALIDINPUTCOLUMNTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7078">"%1" 的 ColumnType 屬性無效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7078">The ColumnType property of "%1" is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7079">目前的值超出可接受的值範圍。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7079">The current value is outside the range of acceptable values.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7080">0xC020802D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7080">0xC020802D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7081">-1071611859</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7081">-1071611859</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7082">DTS_E_TXSCD_CANNOTMAPDIFFERENTTYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7082">DTS_E_TXSCD_CANNOTMAPDIFFERENTTYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7083">輸入資料行 "%1" 無法對應到外部資料行 "%2"，因為資料類型不同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7083">The input column "%1" cannot be mapped to external column "%2" because they have different data types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7084">除了 DT_STR 和 DT_WSTR 之外，緩時變維度轉換不允許在不同類型的資料行之間對應。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7084">The Slowly Changing Dimension transform does not allow mapping between column of different types except for DT_STR and DT_WSTR.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7085">0xC020802E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7085">0xC020802E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7086">-1071611858</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7086">-1071611858</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7087">DTS_E_NTEXTDATATYPENOTSUPPORTEDWITHANSIFILES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7087">DTS_E_NTEXTDATATYPENOTSUPPORTEDWITHANSIFILES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7088">"%1" 的資料類型是 DT_NTEXT，但 ANSI 檔案不支援。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7088">The data type for "%1" is DT_NTEXT, which is not supported with ANSI files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7089">請改用 DT_TEXT，並使用資料轉換元件將資料轉換成 DT_NTEXT。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7089">Use DT_TEXT instead and convert the data to DT_NTEXT using the data conversion component.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7090">0xC020802F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7090">0xC020802F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7091">-1071611857</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7091">-1071611857</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7092">DTS_E_TEXTDATATYPENOTSUPPORTEDWITHUNICODEFILES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7092">DTS_E_TEXTDATATYPENOTSUPPORTEDWITHUNICODEFILES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7093">"%1" 的資料類型是 DT_TEXT，但 Unicode 檔案不支援。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7093">The data type for "%1" is DT_TEXT, which is not supported with Unicode files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7094">請改用 DT_NTEXT，並使用資料轉換元件將資料轉換成 DT_TEXT。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7094">Use DT_NTEXT instead and convert the data to DT_TEXT using the data conversion component.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7095">0xC0208030</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7095">0xC0208030</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7096">-1071611856</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7096">-1071611856</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7097">DTS_E_IMAGEDATATYPENOTSUPPORTED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7097">DTS_E_IMAGEDATATYPENOTSUPPORTED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7098">"%1" 的資料類型是 DT_IMAGE，但不受支援。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7098">The data type for "%1" is DT_IMAGE, which is not supported.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7099">請改用 DT_TEXT 或 DT_NTEXT，並使用資料轉換元件在 DT_IMAGE 上轉換資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7099">Use DT_TEXT or DT_NTEXT instead and convert the data from, or to, DT_IMAGE using the data conversion component.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7100">0xC0208031</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7100">0xC0208031</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7101">-1071611855</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7101">-1071611855</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7102">DTS_E_FLATFILEFORMATNOTSUPPORTED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7102">DTS_E_FLATFILEFORMATNOTSUPPORTED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7103">一般檔案連接管理員不支援格式 "%1"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7103">Format "%1" is not supported by Flat File Connection Manager.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7104">支援的格式為 Delimited、FixedWidth、RaggedRight 和 Mixed。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7104">Supported formats are Delimited, FixedWidth, RaggedRight, and Mixed.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7105">0xC0208032</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7105">0xC0208032</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7106">-1071611854</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7106">-1071611854</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7107">DTS_E_EXTRACTORFILENAMECOLUMNNOTSTRING</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7107">DTS_E_EXTRACTORFILENAMECOLUMNNOTSTRING</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7108">"%1" 應該包含檔案名稱，但不是 String 類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7108">The "%1" should contain a file name, but it is not of a String type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7109">0xC0208033</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7109">0xC0208033</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7110">-1071611853</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7110">-1071611853</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7111">DTS_E_EXTRACTORCANTAPPENDTRUNCATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7111">DTS_E_EXTRACTORCANTAPPENDTRUNCATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7112">衝突的屬性設定造成錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7112">Error caused by conflicting property settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7113">"%1" 將 AllowAppend 屬性和 ForceTruncate 屬性同時設定為 TRUE，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7113">The "%1" has both the AllowAppend property and the ForceTruncate property set to TRUE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7114">這兩個屬性不能同時設定為 TRUE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7114">Both properties cannot be set to TRUE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7115">請將兩個屬性的其中一個設定為 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7115">Set one of the two properties to FALSE.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7116">0xC0208034</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7116">0xC0208034</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7117">-1071611852</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7117">-1071611852</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7118">DTS_E_EXTRACTORCOLUMNALREADYREFERENCED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7118">DTS_E_EXTRACTORCOLUMNALREADYREFERENCED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7119">%1 參考資料行識別碼 %2!d!，但 %3 已經參考此資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7119">The %1 references column ID %2!d!, but that column is already referenced by %3.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7120">請從資料行的兩個參考移除其中一個。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7120">Remove one of the two reference to the column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7121">0xC0208035</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7121">0xC0208035</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7122">-1071611851</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7122">-1071611851</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7123">DTS_E_CONNECTIONMANANGERNOTASSIGNED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7123">DTS_E_CONNECTIONMANANGERNOTASSIGNED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7124">連接管理員尚未指派給 %1。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7124">A connection manager has not been assigned to the %1.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7125">0xC0208036</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7125">0xC0208036</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7126">-1071611850</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7126">-1071611850</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7127">DTS_E_INSERTERCOLUMNALREADYREFERENCED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7127">DTS_E_INSERTERCOLUMNALREADYREFERENCED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7128">%1 參考識別碼為 %2!d! 的輸出資料行，但 %3 已經參考此資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7128">The %1 references the output column with ID %2!d!, but that column is already referenced by %3.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7129">0xC0208037</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7129">0xC0208037</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7130">-1071611849</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7130">-1071611849</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7131">DTS_E_INSERTERCOLUMNNOTREFERENCED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7131">DTS_E_INSERTERCOLUMNNOTREFERENCED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7132">沒有任何輸入資料行參考 "%1"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7132">The "%1" is not referenced by any input column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7133">每一個輸出資料行必須只由一個輸入資料行參考。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7133">Each output column must be referenced by exactly one input column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7134">0xC0208038</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7134">0xC0208038</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7135">-1071611848</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7135">-1071611848</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7136">DTS_E_INSERTERDATACOLUMNNOTBLOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7136">DTS_E_INSERTERDATACOLUMNNOTBLOB</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7137">"%1" 參考 "%2"，但此資料行不是正確類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7137">The "%1" references "%2", and that column is not the correct type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7138">必須是 DT_TEXT、DT_NTEXT 或 DT_IMAGE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7138">It must be DT_TEXT, DT_NTEXT, or DT_IMAGE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7139">參考指向的資料行必須是 BLOB 類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7139">A reference points to a column that must be a BLOB.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7140">0xC0208039</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7140">0xC0208039</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7141">-1071611847</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7141">-1071611847</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7142">DTS_E_INSERTERFILENAMECOLUMNNOTSTRING</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7142">DTS_E_INSERTERFILENAMECOLUMNNOTSTRING</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7143">"%1" 應該包含檔案名稱，但不是 String 類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7143">The "%1" should contain a file name, but it is not a String type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7144">0xC020803A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7144">0xC020803A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7145">-1071611846</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7145">-1071611846</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7146">DTS_E_INSERTEREXPECTBOMINVALIDTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7146">DTS_E_INSERTEREXPECTBOMINVALIDTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7147">"%1" 將 %2 的 ExpectBOM 屬性設定為 TRUE，但是資料行並非 NT_NTEXT。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7147">The "%1" has the ExpectBOM property set to TRUE for %2, but the column is not NT_NTEXT.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7148">ExpectBOM 指定匯入資料行轉換必須有位元組順序標記 (BOM)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7148">The ExpectBOM specifies that the Import Column transformation expects a byte-order mark (BOM).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7149">請將 ExpectBOM 屬性設定為 False，或將輸出資料行資料類型變更為 DT_NTEXT。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7149">Either set the ExpectBOM property to false or change the output column data type to DT_NTEXT.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7150">0xC020803B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7150">0xC020803B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7151">-1071611845</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7151">-1071611845</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7152">DTS_E_INSERTERINVALIDDATACOLUMNSETTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7152">DTS_E_INSERTERINVALIDDATACOLUMNSETTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7153">資料輸出資料行必須是 DT_TEXT、DT_NTEXT 或 DT_IMAGE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7153">Data output columns must be DT_TEXT, DT_NTEXT, or DT_IMAGE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7154">資料輸出資料行只能設定為 BLOB 類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7154">The data output column may only be set to a BLOB type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7155">0xC020803C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7155">0xC020803C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7156">-1071611844</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7156">-1071611844</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7157">DTS_E_TXSCD_FIXEDATTRIBUTECHANGE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7157">DTS_E_TXSCD_FIXEDATTRIBUTECHANGE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7158">如果 FailOnFixedAttributeChange 屬性 (Property) 設定為 TRUE，當偵測到固定屬性 (Attribute) 變更時，轉換將失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7158">If the FailOnFixedAttributeChange property is set to TRUE, the transformation will fail when a fixed attribute change is detected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7159">如果要將資料列傳送到固定屬性 (Attribute) 輸出，請將 FailOnFixedAttributeChange 屬性 (Property) 設定為 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7159">To send rows to the Fixed Attribute output, set the FailOnFixedAttributeChange property to FALSE.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7160">0xC020803D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7160">0xC020803D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7161">-1071611843</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7161">-1071611843</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7162">DTS_E_TXSCD_LOOKUPFAILURE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7162">DTS_E_TXSCD_LOOKUPFAILURE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7163">查閱轉換無法擷取任何資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7163">The Lookup transformation failed to retrieve any rows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7164">當 FailOnLookupFailure 設定為 TRUE 時，轉換會失敗，不會擷取任何資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7164">The transform fails when the FailOnLookupFailure is set to TRUE and no rows are retrieved.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7165">0xC020803E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7165">0xC020803E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7166">-1071611842</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7166">-1071611842</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7167">DTS_E_TXSCD_INVALIDNUMBERSOFPARAMETERS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7167">DTS_E_TXSCD_INVALIDNUMBERSOFPARAMETERS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7168">在緩時變維度轉換的輸入上，至少必須有一個 Key 類型的資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7168">There must be at least one column type of Key on the input of a Slowly Changing Dimension transformation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7169">請至少將一個資料行類型設定為 Key。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7169">Set at least one column type to Key.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7170">0xC020803F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7170">0xC020803F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7171">-1071611841</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7171">-1071611841</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7172">DTS_E_TXSCD_CANNOTFINDEXTERNALCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7172">DTS_E_TXSCD_CANNOTFINDEXTERNALCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7173">找不到名稱為 "%1" 的外部資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7173">Cannot find external column with name "%1".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7174">0xC0208040</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7174">0xC0208040</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7175">-1071611840</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7175">-1071611840</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7176">DTS_E_TXSCD_INFFEREDINDICATORNOTBOOL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7176">DTS_E_TXSCD_INFFEREDINDICATORNOTBOOL</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7177">推斷的指標資料行 "%1" 必須是 DT_BOOL 類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7177">Inferred indicator column "%1" must be of type DT_BOOL.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7182">0xC0208108</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7182">0xC0208108</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7183">-1071611640</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7183">-1071611640</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7184">DTS_E_TRUNCROWDISPMUSTBENOTUSED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7184">DTS_E_TRUNCROWDISPMUSTBENOTUSED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7185">%1 必須將截斷資料列配置值設定為 RD_NotUsed。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7185">The %1 must have its truncation row disposition value set to RD_NotUsed.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7715">0xC02082FE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7715">0xC02082FE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7716">-1071611138</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7716">-1071611138</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7717">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTCASEJAPANESE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7717">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTCASEJAPANESE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7718">資料行 "%1" 結合日文字元的作業和大小寫作業。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7718">Column "%1" combines operations on Japanese characters with uppercase and lowercase operations.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7719">0xC02082FF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7719">0xC02082FF</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7720">-1071611137</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7720">-1071611137</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7721">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTBOTHCASE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7721">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTBOTHCASE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7722">資料行 "%1" 將資料行同時對應到大寫和小寫。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7722">Column "%1" maps the column to both uppercase and lowercase.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7723">0xC0208300</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7723">0xC0208300</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7724">-1071611136</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7724">-1071611136</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7725">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTLINGUISTIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7725">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTLINGUISTIC</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7726">資料行 "%1" 結合大小寫以外的旗標和語言大小寫作業。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7726">Column "%1" combines flags other than uppercase and lowercase with the linguistic casing operation.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7727">0xC0208301</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7727">0xC0208301</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7728">-1071611135</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7728">-1071611135</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7729">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_INVALIDMAPFLAGANDDATATYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7729">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_INVALIDMAPFLAGANDDATATYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7730">無法依指定來對應資料行 "%1" 的資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7730">The data type of column "%1" cannot be mapped as specified.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7731">0xC0208302</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7731">0xC0208302</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7732">-1071611134</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7732">-1071611134</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7733">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNSUPPORTED_MATCH_INDEX_VERSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7733">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNSUPPORTED_MATCH_INDEX_VERSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7734">不支援已存在的比對索引 "%2" 的版本 (%1)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7734">The version (%1) of the pre-existing match index "%2" is not supported.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7735">需要的版本是 "%3"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7735">The version expected is "%3".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7736">如果索引中繼資料保存的版本不符合用來建立目前程式碼的版本，就會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7736">This error occurs if the version persisted in the index metadata does not match the version which the current code was built for.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7737">請使用目前程式碼版本重建索引，修正錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7737">Fix the error by rebuilding the index with the current version of the code.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7738">0xC0208303</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7738">0xC0208303</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7739">-1071611133</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7739">-1071611133</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7740">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_MATCH_INDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7740">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_MATCH_INDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7741">資料表 "%1" 似乎不是有效的預先建立比對索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7741">The table "%1" does not appear to be a valid pre-built match index.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7742">當無法從指定的預先建立索引載入中繼資料記錄時，就會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7742">This error occurs if the metadata record cannot be loaded from the specified pre-built index.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7743">0xC0208304</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7743">0xC0208304</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7744">-1071611132</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7744">-1071611132</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7745">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLE_TO_READ_MATCH_INDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7745">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLE_TO_READ_MATCH_INDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7746">無法讀取指定的預先建立比對索引 "%1"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7746">Unable to read specified pre-built match index "%1".</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7747">OLEDB 錯誤碼：0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7747">OLEDB Error code: 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7748">0xC0208305</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7748">0xC0208305</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7749">-1071611131</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7749">-1071611131</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7750">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_JOIN_COLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7750">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_JOIN_COLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7751">沒有具有參考資料表資料行之有效聯結的輸入資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7751">There were no input columns with a valid join to a reference table column.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7752">請確定至少有一個聯結是使用輸入資料行屬性 JoinToReferenceColumn 和 JoinType 所定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7752">Make sure that there is at least one join defined using the input column properties JoinToReferenceColumn and JoinType.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7753">0xC0208306</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7753">0xC0208306</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7754">-1071611130</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7754">-1071611130</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7755">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEX_DOES_NOT_CONTAIN_COLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7755">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEX_DOES_NOT_CONTAIN_COLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7756">指定已存在的比對索引 "%1" 最初不是以資料行 "%2" 的模糊相符資訊建立。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7756">The specified pre-existing match index "%1" was not originally built with fuzzy match information for column "%2".</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7757">必須重建來包含這項資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7757">It must be rebuilt to include this information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7758">當用來建立索引的資料行不是模糊聯結資料行時，就會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7758">This error occurs when the index was built with the column not being a fuzzy join column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7759">0xC0208307</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7759">0xC0208307</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7760">-1071611129</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7760">-1071611129</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7761">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_IDENTIFIER_PROPERTY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7761">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_IDENTIFIER_PROPERTY</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7762">提供給屬性 "%2" 的名稱 "%1" 不是有效的 SQL 識別碼名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7762">The name "%1" given for property "%2" is not a valid SQL identifier name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7763">如果屬性的名稱不符合有效 SQL 識別碼名稱的規格時，就會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7763">This error occurs if the name for the property does not conform to the specifications for a valid SQL identifier name.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7764">0xC0208309</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7764">0xC0208309</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7765">-1071611127</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7765">-1071611127</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7766">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MINSIMILARITY_INVALID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7766">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MINSIMILARITY_INVALID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7767">模糊查閱轉換的 MinSimilarity 臨界值屬性必須是大於或等於 0.0 但小於 1.0 的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7767">The MinSimilarity threshold property on the Fuzzy Lookup transformation must be a value greater than or equal to 0.0 but less than 1.0.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7768">0xC020830A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7768">0xC020830A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7769">-1071611126</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7769">-1071611126</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7770">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_PROPERTY_VALUE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7770">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_PROPERTY_VALUE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7771">屬性 "%2" 的值 "%1" 無效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7771">The value "%1" for property "%2" is not valid.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7772">0xC020830B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7772">0xC020830B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7773">-1071611125</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7773">-1071611125</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7774">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_FUZZY_JOIN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7774">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_FUZZY_JOIN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7775">在輸入資料行 "%1" 和參考資料行 "%2" 之間指定的模糊查閱無效，因為只有在類型 DT_STR 和 DT_WSTR 的字串資料行之間，才支援模糊聯結。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7775">The fuzzy lookup specified between input column "%1" and reference column "%2" is not valid because fuzzy joins are only supported between string columns, types DT_STR and DT_WSTR.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7776">0xC020830C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7776">0xC020830C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7777">-1071611124</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7777">-1071611124</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7778">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_EXACT_JOIN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7778">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_EXACT_JOIN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7779">完全查閱資料行 "%1" 和 "%2" 沒有相等的資料類型，或兩者是無法比較的字串類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7779">The exact lookup columns, "%1" and "%2", do not have equal data types or are not comparable string types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7780">在具有相等資料類型或 DT_STR 和 DT_WSTR 組合的資料行之間，支援完全聯結。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7780">Exact joins are supported between columns with equal data types or a DT_STR and DT_WSTR combination.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7781">0xC020830D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7781">0xC020830D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7782">-1071611123</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7782">-1071611123</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7783">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_COPYCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7783">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_COPYCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7784">複製資料行 "%1" 和 "%2" 沒有相等的資料類型，或兩者不是可完整轉換的字串類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7784">The copy columns, "%1" and "%2", do not have equal data types or are not trivially convertible string types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7785">如果在具有相等資料類型或 DT_STR 和 DT_WSTR 組合的資料行之間，支援從參考複製到輸出，但不支援其他類型，就會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7785">This occurs because copying from reference to output between columns with equal data types, or a DT_STR and DT_WSTR combination, is supported, but other types are not.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7786">0xC020830E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7786">0xC020830E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7787">-1071611122</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7787">-1071611122</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7788">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_PASSTHRUCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7788">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_PASSTHRUCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7789">通過資料行 "%1" 和 "%2" 沒有相等的資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7789">The passthrough columns, "%1" and "%2", do not have equal data types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7790">只有相等資料類型的資料行，才支援做為輸入到輸出之間的通過資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7790">Only columns with equal data types are supported as passthrough columns from input to output.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7791">0xC020830F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7791">0xC020830F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7792">-1071611121</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7792">-1071611121</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7793">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLETOLOCATEREFCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7793">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLETOLOCATEREFCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7794">找不到參考資料行 "%1"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7794">Cannot locate reference column "%1".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7795">0xC0208311</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7795">0xC0208311</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7796">-1071611119</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7796">-1071611119</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7797">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_OUTPUT_COLUMN_MUST_BE_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_OR_A_COPY_COLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7797">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_OUTPUT_COLUMN_MUST_BE_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_OR_A_COPY_COLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7798">輸出資料行必須只指定一個 CopyColumn 或 PassThruColumn 屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7798">An output column must have exactly one CopyColumn or PassThruColumn property specified.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7799">當 CopyColumn 和 PassThruColumn 屬性同時設定或同時不設定為非空白值時，就會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7799">This error occurs when neither the CopyColumn or the PassThruColumn properties, or both the CopyColumn and PassThruColumn properties, are set to non-empty values.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7800">0xC0208312</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7800">0xC0208312</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7801">-1071611118</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7801">-1071611118</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7802">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7802">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7803">在輸入資料行集合中，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7803">The source lineage id '%1!d!'</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7804">找不到對輸出資料行 '%3' 的屬性 '%2' 所指定的來源歷程識別碼 '%1!d!'。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7804">specified for property '%2' on output column '%3' was not found in the input column collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7805">在輸入集內找不到輸出資料行上指定為通過資料行的輸入資料行識別碼時，就會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7805">This occurs when the input column id specified on an output column as a passthrough column is not found in the set of inputs.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7806">0xC0208313</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7806">0xC0208313</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7807">-1071611117</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7807">-1071611117</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7808">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEXED_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND_IN_REF_TABLE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7808">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEXED_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND_IN_REF_TABLE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7809">在參考資料表/查詢中，找不到在預先建立之索引 "%2" 中的資料行 "%1"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7809">The column "%1" in the pre-built index "%2" was not found in the reference table/query.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7810">在預先存在的比對索引建立之後，如果參考資料表的結構描述/查詢已變更，就會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7810">This happens if the schema/query of the reference table has changed since the pre-existing match index was built.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7811">0xC0208314</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7811">0xC0208314</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7812">-1071611116</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7812">-1071611116</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7813">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TOKEN_TOO_LONG</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7813">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TOKEN_TOO_LONG</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7814">元件遇到大於 2147483647 個字元的 Token。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7814">The component encountered a token that was larger than 2147483647 characters.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7815">0xC0208315</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7815">0xC0208315</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7816">-1071611115</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7816">-1071611115</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7817">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7817">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7818">無法附加輸出檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7818">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7819">資料行 "%1" 的名稱相符，但是檔案中的資料行類型為 %2，而輸入資料行的類型為 %3。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7819">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has type %2 and the input column has type %3.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7820">資料行中繼資料的資料類型不符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7820">The metadata for the column does not match on data type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7821">0xC0208316</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7821">0xC0208316</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7822">-1071611114</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7822">-1071611114</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7823">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSIZE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7823">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSIZE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7824">無法附加輸出檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7824">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7825">資料行 "%1" 是依名稱比對，但檔案中的資料行最大長度是 %2!d!，而輸入資料行的最大長度則是 %3!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7825">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has maximum length %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7826">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7826">and the input column has maximum length %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7827">資料行的中繼資料長度不相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7827">The metadata for the column does not match in length.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7828">0xC0208317</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7828">0xC0208317</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7829">-1071611113</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7829">-1071611113</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7830">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHCODEPAGE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7830">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHCODEPAGE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7831">無法附加輸出檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7831">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7832">資料行 "%1" 依名稱比對，但檔案中的資料行具有字碼頁 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7832">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has code page %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7833">輸入資料行具有字碼頁 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7833">and the input column has code page %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7834">具名資料行中繼資料的字碼頁不符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7834">The metadata for the named column does not match on code page.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7835">0xC0208318</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7835">0xC0208318</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7836">-1071611112</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7836">-1071611112</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7837">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHPRECISION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7837">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHPRECISION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7838">無法附加輸出檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7838">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7839">資料行 "%1" 依名稱比對，但檔案中的資料行的有效位數是 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7839">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has precision %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7840">輸入資料行的有效位數是 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7840">and the input column has precision %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7841">具名資料行中繼資料的有效位數不符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7841">The metadata for the named column does not match on precision.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7842">0xC0208319</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7842">0xC0208319</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7843">-1071611111</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7843">-1071611111</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7844">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSCALE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7844">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSCALE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7845">無法附加輸出檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7845">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7846">資料行 "%1" 依名稱比對，但檔案中的資料行的小數位數是 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7846">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has scale %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7847">輸入資料行的小數位數是 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7847">and the input column has scale %3!d!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7848">具名資料行中繼資料的小數位數不符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7848">The metadata for the named column does not match on scale.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7854">0xC020831B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7854">0xC020831B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7855">-1071611109</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7855">-1071611109</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7856">DTS_E_INCORRECT_SQL_SERVER_VERSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7856">DTS_E_INCORRECT_SQL_SERVER_VERSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7857">不支援 "%1" 的 DBMS 類型或版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7857">The DBMS type or version of "%1" is not supported.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7858">需要與 Microsoft SQL Server 8.0 版或更新版本之間的連接。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7858">A connection to Microsoft SQL Server version 8.0 or later is required.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7859">如果在連接上的 IDBProperties 未傳回正確的版本，就會發生這個問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7859">This occurs if IDBProperties on the connection did not return a the correct version.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7860">0xC020831D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7860">0xC020831D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7861">-1071611107</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7861">-1071611107</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7862">DTS_E_CANTDELETEERRORCOLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7862">DTS_E_CANTDELETEERRORCOLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7863">%1 是特殊錯誤輸出資料行，不能刪除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7863">The %1 is a special error output column and cannot be deleted.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7864">0xC020831E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7864">0xC020831E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7865">-1071611106</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7865">-1071611106</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7866">DTS_E_UNEXPECTEDCOLUMNDATATYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7866">DTS_E_UNEXPECTEDCOLUMNDATATYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7867">對資料行 "%1" 指定的資料類型不是預期的類型 "%2"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7867">The data type specified for column "%1" is not the expected type "%2".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7868">0xC020831F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7868">0xC020831F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7869">-1071611105</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7869">-1071611105</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7870">DTS_E_INPUTCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7870">DTS_E_INPUTCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7871">在輸入資料行集合中，找不到輸入資料行歷程識別碼 "%1"，此歷程識別碼是由輸出資料行 "%3" 上的屬性 "%2" 所參照。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7871">The input column lineage ID "%1" referenced by property "%2" on output column "%3" could not be located in the input column collection.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7872">0xC0208320</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7872">0xC0208320</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7873">-1071611104</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7873">-1071611104</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7874">DTS_E_TXGROUPDUPS_INPUTCOLUMNNOTJOINED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7874">DTS_E_TXGROUPDUPS_INPUTCOLUMNNOTJOINED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7875">由輸出資料行 "%3" 上的 "%2" 屬性所參考的輸入資料行 "%1" 必須有屬性 ToBeCleaned=True，而且有一個有效 ExactFuzzy 屬性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7875">The input column "%1" referenced by the "%2" property on output column "%3" must have property ToBeCleaned=True and have a valid ExactFuzzy property value.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7876">0xC0208322</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7876">0xC0208322</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7877">-1071611102</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7877">-1071611102</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7878">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_TABLE_MISSING_IDENTITY_INDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7878">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_TABLE_MISSING_IDENTITY_INDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7879">參考資料表 '%1' 在整數識別欄位上沒有叢集索引，但如果屬性 'CopyRefTable' 設定為 FALSE，則需要這個索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7879">The reference table '%1' does not have a clustered index on an integer identity column, which is required if the property 'CopyRefTable' is set to FALSE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7880">如果 CopyRefTable 是 false，則參考資料表在整數識別欄位上必須有叢集索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7880">If CopyRefTable is false, the reference table must have a clustered index on an integer identity column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7881">0xC0208323</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7881">0xC0208323</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7882">-1071611101</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7882">-1071611101</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7883">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_CONTAINS_NON_INTEGER_IDENT_COLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7883">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_CONTAINS_NON_INTEGER_IDENT_COLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7884">參考資料表 '%1' 包含非整數類型的識別欄位，但並不支援。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7884">The reference table '%1' contains a non-integer type identity column which is not supported.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7885">請使用資料表的檢視，且檢視不包含資料行 '%2'。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7885">Use a view of the table without the column '%2'.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7886">當建立參考資料表的副本時，因為會加入整數識別欄位，但每個資料表僅允許一個識別欄位，所以會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7886">This error occurs  because when a copy is made of the reference table, an integer identity column is added, and only one identity column is allowed per table.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7887">0xC0208324</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7887">0xC0208324</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7888">-1071611100</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7888">-1071611100</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7889">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_MATCHCONTRIBUTION_AND_HIERARCHY_SPECIFIED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7889">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_MATCHCONTRIBUTION_AND_HIERARCHY_SPECIFIED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7890">不能同時指定 MatchContribution 和階層資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7890">Both MatchContribution and hierarchy information cannot be specified at the same time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7891">這是不允許的，因為這兩個屬性都是計分加權因數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7891">This is not allowed because these properties are both weighing factors for scoring.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7892">0xC0208325</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7892">0xC0208325</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7893">-1071611099</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7893">-1071611099</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7894">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_HIERARCHY_INCORRECT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7894">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_HIERARCHY_INCORRECT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7895">階層的層級必須是唯一的數字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7895">Levels in hierarchy should be unique numbers .</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7896">階層值的有效層級是大於或等於 1 的整數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7896">Valid  level in hierarchy values are integers greater than or equal to 1.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7897">數字愈小，資料行在階層中的位置愈低。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7897">The smaller the number is, the lower the column is in the hierarchy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7898">預設值是 0，表示資料行不是階層的一部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7898">The default value is 0, indicating that the column is not part of a hierarchy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7899">不允許重疊和間隔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7899">Overlaps and gaps are not allowed.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7900">0xC0208326</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7900">0xC0208326</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7901">-1071611098</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7901">-1071611098</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7902">DTS_E_TXFUZZYGROUPING_INSUFFICIENT_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7902">DTS_E_TXFUZZYGROUPING_INSUFFICIENT_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7903">未定義要進行模糊群組的資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7903">No columns to fuzzy group on were defined.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7904">至少必須要有一個輸入資料行的資料行屬性為 ToBeCleaned=true 和 ExactFuzzy=2。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7904">There must be at least one input column with column properties ToBeCleaned=true and ExactFuzzy=2.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7905">0xC0208329</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7905">0xC0208329</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7906">-1071611095</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7906">-1071611095</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7907">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_COLUMNINVALID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7907">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_COLUMNINVALID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-7908">識別碼為 '%1!d!' 的資料行</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7908">The column with ID '%1!d!'</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-7909">無效，原因不明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-7909">was not valid for an undetermined reason.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9681">0x80047069</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9681">0x80047069</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9682">-2147192727</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9682">-2147192727</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9683">DTS_W_SORTEDOUTPUTHASNOSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9683">DTS_W_SORTEDOUTPUTHASNOSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9684">%1 的 IsSorted 屬性設定為 TRUE，但所有輸出資料行的 SortKeyPositions 設定為零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9684">The IsSorted property of %1 is set to TRUE, but all of its output columns' SortKeyPositions are set to zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9685">0x8004706F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9685">0x8004706F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9686">-2147192721</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9686">-2147192721</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9687">DTS_W_SOURCEREMOVED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9687">DTS_W_SOURCEREMOVED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9688">將不會讀取來源 "%1" (%2!d!)，因為在資料流程工作之外無法看到任何資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9688">Source "%1" (%2!d!) will not be read because none of its data ever becomes visible outside the Data Flow Task.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9689">0x80047076</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9689">0x80047076</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9690">-2147192714</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9690">-2147192714</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9691">DTS_W_UNUSEDOUTPUTDATA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9691">DTS_W_UNUSEDOUTPUTDATA</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9692">資料流程工作後續未使用輸出 "%3" (%4!d!) 和元件 "%5" (%6!d!) 的輸出資料行 "%1" (%2!d!)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9692">The output column "%1" (%2!d!) on output "%3" (%4!d!) and component "%5" (%6!d!) is not subsequently used in the Data Flow task.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9693">移除這個未使用的輸出資料行可以提升資料流程工作的效能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9693">Removing this unused output column can increase Data Flow task performance.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9694">0x800470AE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9694">0x800470AE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9695">-2147192658</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9695">-2147192658</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9696">DTS_W_COMPONENTREMOVED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9696">DTS_W_COMPONENTREMOVED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9697">已從資料流程工作移除元件 "%1" (%2!d!)，因為沒有用到輸出，而且輸入沒有副作用或未連接到其他元件的輸出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9697">Component "%1" (%2!d!) has been removed from the Data Flow task because its output is not used and its inputs either have no side effects or are not connected to outputs of other components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9698">如果需要此元件，則至少其中一個輸入的 HasSideEffects 屬性應該設定為 true，或輸出應該連接某些目標。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9698">If the component is required, then the HasSideEffects property on at least one of its inputs should be set to true, or its output should be connected to something.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9728">0x800470E9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9728">0x800470E9</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9729">-2147192599</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9729">-2147192599</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9730">DTS_W_COMPONENTLEAKPROCESSINPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9730">DTS_W_COMPONENTLEAKPROCESSINPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9731">對 %2 上的輸入 %1!d! 呼叫 ProcessInput 方法，非預期地保留傳遞緩衝區的參考</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9731">A call to the ProcessInput method for input %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9732">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9732">on %2 unexpectedly kept a reference to the buffer it was passed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9733">在呼叫前，該緩衝區的 refcount 是 %3!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9733">The refcount on that buffer was %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9734">呼叫傳回後變成 %4!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9734">before the call, and %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9735">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9735">after the call returned.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9782">0x8020400D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9782">0x8020400D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9783">-2145370099</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9783">-2145370099</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9784">DTS_W_NOPIPELINEDATATYPEMAPPINGAVAILABLE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9784">DTS_W_NOPIPELINEDATATYPEMAPPINGAVAILABLE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9785">%1 參考的外部資料類型無法對應至資料流程工作資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9785">The %1 references an external data type that cannot be mapped to a Data Flow task data type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9786">將改用資料流程工作資料類型 DT_WSTR。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9786">The Data Flow task data type DT_WSTR will be used instead.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9787">0x802070CC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9787">0x802070CC</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9788">-2145357620</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9788">-2145357620</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9789">DTS_W_STATICTRUNCATIONINEXPRESSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9789">DTS_W_STATICTRUNCATIONINEXPRESSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9790">運算式 "%1" 永遠會導致資料截斷。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9790">The expression "%1" will always result in a truncation of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9791">運算式包含靜態截斷 (固定值的截斷)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9791">The expression contains a static truncation (the truncation of a fixed value).</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9792">0x8020820C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9792">0x8020820C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9793">-2145353204</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9793">-2145353204</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9794">DTS_W_UNMAPPEDINPUTCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9794">DTS_W_UNMAPPEDINPUTCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9795">在索引 %3!d!，識別碼為 %2!d! 的</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9795">The input column "%1" with ID %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9796">輸入資料行 "%1"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9796">at index %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9797">未產生對應。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9797">is unmapped.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9798">資料行的歷程識別碼為零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9798">The lineage ID for the column is zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9799">0x80208305</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9799">0x80208305</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9800">-2145352955</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9800">-2145352955</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9801">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_DELIMITERS_DONT_MATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9801">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_DELIMITERS_DONT_MATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9802">指定的分隔符號與用來建立已存在之比對索引 "%1" 的分隔符號不相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9802">The specified delimiters do not match the delimiters used to build the pre-existing match index "%1".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9803">當用來 Token 化欄位的分隔符號不符時，就會發生這個錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9803">This error occurs when the delimiters used to tokenize fields do not match.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9804">這對於比對行為或結果會產生未知的影響。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9804">This can have unknown effects on the matching behavior or results.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9805">0x80208308</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9805">0x80208308</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9806">-2145352952</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9806">-2145352952</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9807">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MAXRESULTS_IS_ZERO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9807">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MAXRESULTS_IS_ZERO</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9808">模糊查閱轉換的 MaxOutputMatchesPerInput 屬性為零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9808">The MaxOutputMatchesPerInput property on the Fuzzy Lookup transformation is zero.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9809">將不會產生結果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9809">No results will be produced.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9810">0x80208310</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9810">0x80208310</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9811">-2145352944</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9811">-2145352944</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9812">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9812">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9813">沒有具有 JoinType 資料行屬性設定為模糊的有效輸入資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9813">There were no valid input columns with JoinType column property set to Fuzzy.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9814">使用查詢轉換取代模糊查詢，可以改善完全聯結的效能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9814">Performance on Exact joins may be improved by using the Lookup transform instead of FuzzyLookup.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9815">0x8020831C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9815">0x8020831C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9816">-2145352932</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9816">-2145352932</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9817">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TIMESTAMPCAVEAT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9817">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TIMESTAMPCAVEAT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9818">參考資料行 "%1" 可能是 SQL 時間戳記資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9818">The reference column "%1" may be a SQL timestamp column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9819">建立了模糊相符索引且製作參考資料表的複本時，所有參考資料表的時間戳記都將反映資料表在複製時的目前狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9819">When the fuzzy match index is built, and a copy of the reference table is made, all reference table timestamps will reflect the current state of the table at the time of the copy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9820">如果 CopyReferenceTable 設定為 False，可能會發生非預期的行為。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9820">Unexpected behavior may occur if the CopyReferenceTable is set to false.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9821">0x80208321</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9821">0x80208321</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9822">-2145352927</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9822">-2145352927</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9823">DTS_W_MATCHINDEXALREADYEXISTS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9823">DTS_W_MATCHINDEXALREADYEXISTS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9824">給予 MatchIndexName 的資料表名稱 '%1' 已經存在，且 DropExistingMatchIndex 設定為 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9824">A table with the name '%1' given for MatchIndexName already exists and DropExistingMatchIndex is set to FALSE.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9825">除非卸除這個資料表、指定不同名稱或將 DropExisitingMatchIndex 設定為 TRUE，否則轉換的執行會失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9825">Transform execution will fail unless this table is dropped, a different name is specified, or DropExisitingMatchIndex is set to TRUE.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9826">0x8020832B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9826">0x8020832B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9827">-2145352917</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9827">-2145352917</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9828">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_JOINLENGTHMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9828">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_JOINLENGTHMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9829">輸入資料行 '%1' 的長度不等於要比對之參考資料行 '%2' 的長度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9829">The length of input column '%1' is not equal to the length of the reference column '%2' that it is being matched against.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9830">0x8020832D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9830">0x8020832D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9831">-2145352915</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9831">-2145352915</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9832">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_CODEPAGE_MISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9832">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_CODEPAGE_MISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9833">DT_STR 來源資料行 "%1" 的字碼頁與 DT_STR 目的地資料行的字碼頁 "%2" 不符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9833">The code pages of the DT_STR source column "%1" and the DT_STR dest column "%2" do not match.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9834">這可能會造成非預期的結果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9834">This may cause unexpected results.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9835">0x8020832E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9835">0x8020832E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9836">-2145352914</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9836">-2145352914</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9837">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_TOOMANYEXACTMATCHCOLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9837">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_TOOMANYEXACTMATCHCOLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9838">有 16 個以上的完全相符聯結，所以可能無法達到最佳效能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9838">There are more than 16 exact match joins, so performance may not be optimal.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9839">請減少完全相符聯結的數目來提升效能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9839">Reduce the number of exact match joins to improve performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9840">SQL Server 限制每個索引最多 16 個資料行，所有查閱將使用反向索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9840">SQL Server has a limit of 16 columns per index, the inverted index will be used for all lookups.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9841">0x80208350</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9841">0x80208350</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9842">-2145352880</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9842">-2145352880</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9843">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_MEMLIMITANDEXHAUSTIVESPECIFIED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9843">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_MEMLIMITANDEXHAUSTIVESPECIFIED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9844">Exhaustive 選項需要將整個參考載入主記憶體中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9844">The Exhaustive option requires that the entire reference be loaded into main memory.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9845">由於已經為 MaxMemoryUsage 屬性指定了記憶體限制，因此整個參考資料表可能超出這個界限，而且比對作業可能會在執行階段失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9845">Since a memory limit has been specified for the MaxMemoryUsage property, it is possible that the entire reference table will not fit within this bound and that the match operation will fail at runtime.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9846">0x80208351</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9846">0x80208351</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9847">-2145352879</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9847">-2145352879</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9848">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHCOLUMNSEXCEEDBYTELIMIT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9848">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHCOLUMNSEXCEEDBYTELIMIT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9849">完全相符聯結中指定之資料行的累計長度超過索引鍵的 900 位元組限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9849">The cumulative lengths of the columns specified in the exact match joins exceeds the 900 byte limit for index keys.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9850">模糊查閱會在完全相符資料行上建立索引，藉以提升查閱效能。建立這個索引時有可能失敗，迫使查閱尋求替代方法 (可能較慢) 來尋找相符項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9850">Fuzzy Lookup creates an index on the exact match columns to increase lookup performance and there is a possibility that creation of this index may fail and the lookup will fall back to an alternative, possibly slower, method of finding matches.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9851">如果效能是個問題，請嘗試移除一些完全相符聯結資料行，或縮短變動長度完全相符資料行的最大長度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9851">If performance is a problem, try removing some exact match join columns or reduce the maximum lengths of variable length exact match columns.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9852">0x80208352</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9852">0x80208352</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9853">-2145352878</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9853">-2145352878</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9854">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHINDEXCREATIONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9854">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHINDEXCREATIONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9855">無法建立完全相符資料行的索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9855">Failed to create an index for exact match columns.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9856">返回尋求替代的模糊查閱方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9856">Reverting to alternative fuzzy lookup method.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9857">0x80208353</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9857">0x80208353</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9858">-2145352877</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9858">-2145352877</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9859">DTS_W_FUZZYGROUPINGINTERNALPIPELINEWARNING</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9859">DTS_W_FUZZYGROUPINGINTERNALPIPELINEWARNING</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9860">發生下列模糊群組內部管線警告，警告碼為 0x%1!8.8X!: "%2"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9860">The following Fuzzy Grouping internal pipeline warning occurred with warning code 0x%1!8.8X!: "%2".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9861">0x80208375</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9861">0x80208375</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9862">-2145352843</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9862">-2145352843</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9863">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNLENGTHSETTODEFAULT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9863">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNLENGTHSETTODEFAULT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9864">具有外部資料類型 %2 的 %1 未指定最大長度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9864">No maximum length was specified for the %1 with external data type %2.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9865">將使用長度為 %4!d! 的 SSIS 資料流程工作資料類型 "%3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9865">The SSIS Data Flow Task data type "%3" with a length of %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9866">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9866">will be used.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9867">0x80208376</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9867">0x80208376</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9868">-2145352842</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9868">-2145352842</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9869">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNDATATYPEMAPPEDTOSTRING</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9869">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNDATATYPEMAPPEDTOSTRING</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24b20-9870">%1 參考的外部資料類型 %2 無法對應至 SSIS 資料流程工作資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9870">The %1 references external data type %2, which cannot be mapped to a SSIS Data Flow Task data type.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9871">將改使用長度為 %3!d! 的 SSIS 資料流程工作資料類型 DT_WSTR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9871">The SSIS Data Flow Task data type DT_WSTR with a length of %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24b20-9872">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24b20-9872">will be used instead.</span></span>|
